":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"idb801b6a9-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Level IV or V of the Executive Schedule, referred to in subsec. (a)(2), are set out in sections 5315 and 5316 of this title.","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section 226 of the Homeland Security Act of 2002, referred to in cl. (iii) of concluding provisions of subsec. (a)(2), probably means the ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/107/296/s226"},"text":"section 226 of Pub. L. 107–296","children":[],"tail":" as added by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/113/277/s3/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 113–277, § 3(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2014-12-18"},"text":"Dec. 18, 2014","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/128/3005"},"text":"128 Stat. 3005","children":[],"tail":", which was renumbered "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/107/296/s2208"},"text":"section 2208 of Pub. L. 107–296","children":[],"tail":" by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/278/s2/g/2/I"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–278, § 2(g)(2)(I)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2018-11-16"},"text":"Nov. 16, 2018","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/132/4178"},"text":"132 Stat. 4178","children":[],"tail":", and is classified to "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t6/s658"},"text":"section 658 of Title 6","children":[],"tail":", Domestic Security."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The date of the enactment of the Civil Service Reform Act of 1978, referred to in subsec. (b)(3), is the date of the enactment of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/95/454"},"text":"Pub. L. 95–454","children":[],"tail":", which was approved "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1978-10-13"},"text":"Oct. 13, 1978","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"idb801b6aa-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2015—Subsec. (a)(2). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/114/92"},"text":"Pub. L. 114–92","children":[],"tail":" added cl. (iv) of concluding provisions."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2014—Subsec. (a)(2). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/113/277"},"text":"Pub. L. 113–277","children":[],"tail":" added cl. (iii) of concluding provisions."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2013—Subsec. (a)(1)(B). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/112/277"},"text":"Pub. L. 112–277","children":[],"tail":" inserted “the Office of the Director of National Intelligence,” after “the Central Intelligence Agency,”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2010—Subsec. (a)(1)(D). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/203"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–203","children":[],"tail":" substituted “the National Credit Union Administration, the Bureau of Consumer Financial Protection, and the Office of Financial Research;” for “and the National Credit Union Administration;”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2008—Subsec. (a)(1)(B). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/417"},"text":"Pub. L. 110–417","children":[],"tail":" substituted “National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency” for “National Imagery and Mapping Agency”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/289/s1161/g/2/A"},"text":"Pub. L. 110–289, § 1161(g)(2)(A)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “, and” for “,, and”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (a)(1)(D). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/289/s1161/g/2/B"},"text":"Pub. L. 110–289, § 1161(g)(2)